7,"title":"能否直接连自来水管来进行电脑散热？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/605429167","type":"question","created":1686187179,"answer_count":58,"follower_count":57,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[15119,16140,22258],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"之前看到一个说法：不管是水冷还是风冷，最末端肯定都是要通过风冷的形式把热量散到外面的空气里的。而且，散热的液体也是一直的闭环循环状态，热量也会在内部堆积。那么，可不可以直接把散热的末端接到自来水管上，用持续的水流来带走散热系统最终端的热量，让这个热量顺着水进入下水道。一方面水带走热量要比空气快，另一方面接触到电脑的会一直是新的冷水。至于水费，本身就比电费便宜不少，给电脑冷却的水费比起电脑的电费，应该只是增加了一个小头。当然，这样确实很浪费，不过这里先不讨论这个问题。"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ilb632ajdm74DEAMaCDk2ODE5OTUzIKvZhKQGMAA4OUAMcgk2MDU0MjkxNjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-98defe24b715e65d49609c775da5f86c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1726625758.526319","card_id":"Q_667269250","target":{"id":667269250,"title":"怎样戒掉懒惰，改变自己的坏习惯？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/667269250","type":"question","created":1726414979,"answer_count":141,"follower_count":379,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[22173],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我感觉自己特别懒惰，而且特别拖拉，已经形成习惯了，每次都想着要改，结果还是这样。"},"attached_info":"CkAIlb632ajdm74DEAMaCTExMDU1OTc0OCCDgZy3BjAAOPsCQA1yCTY2NzI2OTI1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"54 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b21458f8fe26c8b0187aec6b36537b89_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1726625758.526537","card_id":"Q_661147305","target":{"id":661147305,"title":"员工每次只打欠薪老板一耳光，躲哪都能找到，打完自首，出狱继续，打几次会转为刑事拘留，最重会被判几年?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/661147305","type":"question","created":1720514759